snippet.title: Mental Healness
snippet.description: Diagnosed mental health sufferer. Been in psychotherapy since October of 2017. The goal of this page is to help others understand that you are not alone and to validate the victims of mental health abuse. Tiktok is my biggest platform as I have accumulated over 1 million followers. I do offer One on Ones to give people the first hand perspective of a narcissist.
